{"tid":2357231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港中央電視台訪問居美香港人間諜：國會暴動顯示美國雙重標準，","createTime":"2021-01-07T09:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T10:02:14.000Z","uid":19527,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4e0566ebb5b39c5bcf51ae89ec4363c53be549c6","tid":2357231,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nS0bEeX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnS0bEeX.jpg&h=528dcc4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCCTVB播放fake news已是家常便飯，為避過新聞操守的質疑就直接使用受訪者的soundbite來散播假消息，不加澄清亦可逃避責任。<br />\n<br />\n事實：美國眾議院議長佩洛西從來沒有讚揚香港示威者衝入立法會，她形容為「美麗的風景線(a beautiful sight to behold)」的，是指2019年6月4日維園六四燭光晚會。<br />\n<br />\n另外也想勸喻王太，既然覺得美國這麼雙重標準，請不要繼續在美國過著如煉獄般的日子，馬上舉家移民到粵港澳大灣區，享受中國人沒有示威沒有抗議的和諧生活。<br />\n<br />\n#只要受訪者批評美國就可以令CCTVB高潮<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/453118411470994/posts/3622338707882266/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F453118411470994%2Fposts%2F3622338707882266%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6zxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=f6356535\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/453118411470994/posts/3622338707882266/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"fe7d0ec90ea54bd1cae882bf275ec2cb11156185","tid":2357231,"uid":2757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hs5JHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hs5JHq.jpg&h=820f153d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c163d2a92bb22b350967c9401b1e0d5f5425bb9","tid":2357231,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"美國好差 快啲返去中国<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760b7f373583efdfa085f171a2edfa57365edeab","tid":2357231,"uid":259520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"起底組,有無本事起到佢底??"},{"pid":"decfc2dec9